e second industrial revolution and the rise of the welfare state.  afunded by Knowledge Unlatched  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 7aHISTORY / Modern / General.2bisacsh2 aKnowledge Unlatchedefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBerghahn Books Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z9783110998238oZDB-23-BHBO40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781785336607?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781785336607zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781785336607/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-BHBOc2014d2015  aZDB-23-GOA